sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as FastAPI Server
    participant A as Auth Middleware
    participant R as RAG Engine
    participant D as Diagram Agent
    C->>API: POST /generate {text_description, diagram_type}
    API->>A: Validate authentication
    A-->>API: Auth valid
    API->>D: Generate diagram
    D->>R: Fetch data
    R-->>D: Data retrieved
    D-->>API: Return mermaid_code
    API-->>C: 200 OK {mermaid_code}